  "description": "A close-up shot features a large, dark, rocky outcrop covered in barnacles and seaweed, partially submerged in shallow, turquoise water. The rock is heavily textured with a dense collection of small, white barnacles clinging to its surface. Patches of green algae or seaweed add further color variation. The background showcases a deeper blue ocean with several distant rock formations rising from the water, suggesting an island or coastal scenery. The waves are gently breaking in the distance, creating white foam. The overall scene evokes a sense of the rugged beauty of a rocky coastline.",
